milestones.description: Srinath and Ajay Jadeja's 62-run partnership is IND's highest for the 10th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 53 between Ravi Shastri and Hirwani

stories.title: 1st Match,India v South Africa,Coca-Cola Cup,Statistical Highlights
stories.summary: It was the 1577th ODI in cricket history

stories.title: Indian middle order is strong, but can be brittle at times
stories.summary:
The psychological advantage the Indians had over the South Africans
was annulled ruthlessly by the Springboks in the lung opener of the
Coca-Cola Championship at Sharjah

stories.title: South Africa smother India in CCC opener
stories.summary: Very few matches go down to the last ball of the second innings
